          <p class="c2 c5"><span class="c0"></span></p>
          <p class="c2">
            <span class="c0"
              >&ldquo;Jing was one of the first people I met in the astronomy
              department. We were in a breakout room together on a Zoom call and
              we started talking about sci-fi novels we read and found a common
              interest there. We communicated several times after this about the
